==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: living room
<hw>liv"ing room`</hw>. <def>A room in a house used by all or most of
the family, where the family entertain guests or relax together for
leisure activities. It usually contains at least one couch, and does not
contain a dining table.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>living wage</ent>⟦br⟧
